Overview

This dashboard shows Suspicions Process overview related to the Cybereason Integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the ingested Suspicions Process logs from Cybereason.

It displays the aggregate count of malicious and non-malicious suspicions. It shows the breakdown of Suspicions Process by suspect and product type. It presents the distribution of Suspicions Process events across creation time. The dashboard also includes the top 10 Suspicions Parent Process. In addition, it illustrates the essential details of Suspicions Process.
